{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"B\n    \n      High-Detail Top-Down Sprites\n      Generate unique 8-bit top-down sprites for every car in your garage. Not generic colored rectangles — actual pixel art showing the body shape, hood scoops, racing stripes, spoilers, convertible tops down. A Corvette looks nothing like a lifted truck. Each one is a tiny work of art on the track.","choice":"topdown-sprites","id":null,"timestamp":1775273211080}
{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"A\n    \n      Cockpit HUD Overlay\n      A translucent dashboard strip along the bottom edge — unique per car. Shows the actual gauge cluster, steering wheel silhouette, and interior color. A '69 Camaro gets orange-lit round gauges; a Tesla gets a minimalist screen. You're looking down at the track but your car's personality is always in your peripheral vision.","choice":"cockpit-hud","id":null,"timestamp":1775273212564}
