{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"1\n    \n      Lakefront Sprint\n      Route: Teckler Blvd → Route 14 → Crystal Lake Ave → Dole Ave → Lakeshore Drive → finish at Main Beach\n      Vibe: Starts industrial, transitions through tree-lined residential streets, ends at the lake with water reflections and the Dole Mansion in the background. Sunset palette — golden hour over the water.\n      Hazards: Sharp turn onto Dole Ave, narrow lakeside road, pedestrians near the beach\n      The signature track. Short, scenic, emotional finish at the water.","choice":"lakefront","id":null,"timestamp":1775273948359}
{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"2\n    \n      Downtown Dash\n      Route: Teckler Blvd → Route 14 → Williams Street → Crystal Lake Ave → past the Raue Center → through the historic downtown grid → Virginia Street\n      Vibe: Tight small-town streets, brick storefronts, the 1929 Raue Center theater marquee glowing, café tables on sidewalks, street lamps. Night race with neon signs and shop windows.\n      Hazards: Tight corners through the grid, parked cars on Williams St, crosswalks\n      The technical track. Tight turns, small-town charm, lots of pixel art detail.","choice":"downtown","id":null,"timestamp":1775273951175}
